<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="294" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1624,1843]" pageId="4" pageNumber="294">
Distribution. Polytypic species, distributed in the whole of Europe, eastwards as far as the Caucasus and 
<collectingCountry box="[151,256,1701,1727]" name="Turkey" pageId="4" pageNumber="294">Anatolia</collectingCountry>
. The nominal subspecies in 
<collectingCountry box="[588,642,1701,1727]" name="Italy" pageId="4" pageNumber="294">Italy</collectingCountry>
is distributed in the mainland and 
<collectingRegion box="[1052,1122,1701,1727]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="4" pageNumber="294">Sicily</collectingRegion>
. It lives in the leaf litter of broad-leaved woodlands, and occasionally enters natural caves.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1624,1843]" box="[198,457,1778,1804]" pageId="4" pageNumber="294">Chorotype. European.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1624,1843]" box="[198,841,1817,1843]" pageId="4" pageNumber="294">
Remarks. Known so far only from one site in 
<collectingRegion box="[735,836,1817,1843]" country="Italy" name="Sardegna" pageId="4" pageNumber="294">Sardinia</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
